[14/01/2018 02:27:15] <font color="#ffffff">acusado de haberle pasado</font>
[14/01/2018 02:27:15] <font color="#ffffff">información privi..."</font>
[14/01/2018 02:27:19] <font color="#ffff00">(TARAREA)</font>
[14/01/2018 02:27:22] <font color="#00ffff">(TOSE)</font>
[14/01/2018 02:27:56] <font color="#00ffff">Sí, soy yo.</font>
[14/01/2018 02:27:58] <font color="#00ffff">Bien, bien, bien.</font>
